BEGIN_TEXT
$BR
Find the values of x so that the series below converges.
\[
    \sum_{n=0}^\infty \frac{(x + $a)^n}{$b^n}
\]

$BR
Give your answer in interval notation.$BR
\( ( \)\{ans_rule()\}, \{ans_rule()\}\( ) \)


$PAR
END_TEXT

    ANS(num_cmp(-$a - $b));
    ANS(num_cmp(-$a + $b));

